{
  "stem": "2684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Their hair was shaven, which means their head was shaven.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had no hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and as a youngsters, we looked at amazement to what is going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my parents were aware of it, definitely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because when the-- for the-- in front of the children, it wasn't much said.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when adults came to our home, and-- and we were-- had to go to the kitchen while the adults was talking, we heard all the-- all the stories-- what's going on-- but being very young, couldn't comprehend or-- or wouldn't sink in, actually, what is happening.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We read a little bit of newspaper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not because there was no newspaper, but because we read very little newspaper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew that what's happening with Hitler coming on power and-- and-- [BACKROUND NOISE] and what happened in Italy, and-- and Mussolini came to power.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we heard of the Princess of Windsor, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So news was coming in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the early-- late '30s, very early '40s, we were still very well informed about the happening in-- in-- in Europe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as I said in my earlier statement, that I, as a child, did not notice too much, which would affect my life tremendously.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Amongst your friends, or at school, was there any discussion about it?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we played games.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the games, I was always the Englishman, and the non-Jews were the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we fight like hell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And whoever won the fight won the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was-- that-- that's the most we knew about the-- about about [LAUGHS] the world happenings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did not-- we did not discuss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had youngsters who-- who had anti-Semitic tendencies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But fortunately, his mouth was shut in very early times.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
